{
  "video_id": "vEli4dfAXrM",
  "title": "Karen Tse: How to stop torture",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 16260.000000000002,
      "end_time": 20260.0,
      "text": "In 1994, I walked into a prison in Cambodia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 20260.0,
      "end_time": 23260.0,
      "text": "and I met a 12-year-old boy"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 23260.0,
      "end_time": 25260.0,
      "text": "who had been tortured"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 25260.0,
      "end_time": 27260.0,
      "text": "and was denied access to counsel."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27260.0,
      "end_time": 29260.0,
      "text": "And as I looked into his eyes, I realized"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29260.0,
      "end_time": 31260.0,
      "text": "that for the hundreds of letters I had written"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31260.0,
      "end_time": 34260.0,
      "text": "for political prisoners, that I would never have"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34260.0,
      "end_time": 36260.0,
      "text": "written a letter for him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36260.0,
      "end_time": 38260.0,
      "text": "because he was not a 12-year-old boy who"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38260.0,
      "end_time": 40260.0,
      "text": "had done something important for anybody."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40260.0,
      "end_time": 42260.0,
      "text": "He was not a political prisoner."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42260.0,
      "end_time": 44260.0,
      "text": "He was a 12-year-old boy who had"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44260.0,
      "end_time": 46260.0,
      "text": "stolen a bicycle."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46260.0,
      "end_time": 48260.0,
      "text": "What I also realized at that point was that"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 48260.0,
      "end_time": 50260.0,
      "text": "it was not only Cambodia, but"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 50260.0,
      "end_time": 52260.0,
      "text": "of the 113"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 52260.0,
      "end_time": 54260.0,
      "text": "developing countries that torture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 54260.0,
      "end_time": 57260.0,
      "text": "93 of these countries have all passed laws"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 57260.0,
      "end_time": 59260.0,
      "text": "that say you have a right to a lawyer"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 59260.0,
      "end_time": 62260.0,
      "text": "and you have a right not to be tortured."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 62260.0,
      "end_time": 64259.0,
      "text": "And what I recognized was that there was an"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 64260.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66260.0,
      "text": "incredible window of opportunity for us"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 66260.0,
      "end_time": 69260.0,
      "text": "as a world community to come together"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 69260.0,
      "end_time": 72260.0,
      "text": "and end torture as an investigative tool."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 72260.0,
      "end_time": 74260.0,
      "text": "We often think of torture as being"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 74260.0,
      "end_time": 76260.0,
      "text": "political torture or reserved for"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 76260.0,
      "end_time": 79260.0,
      "text": "just the worst, but, in fact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 79260.0,
      "end_time": 81260.0,
      "text": "95 percent of torture today"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 81260.0,
      "end_time": 83260.0,
      "text": "is not for political prisoners."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 83260.0,
      "end_time": 85260.0,
      "text": "It is for people who are"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 85260.0,
      "end_time": 87260.0,
      "text": "in broken-down legal systems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 87260.0,
      "end_time": 89260.0,
      "text": "and unfortunately because torture is"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 89260.0,
      "end_time": 91260.0,
      "text": "the cheapest form of investigation --"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 91260.0,
      "end_time": 93260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s cheaper than having a legal system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 93260.0,
      "end_time": 95260.0,
      "text": "cheaper than having a lawyer"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 95260.0,
      "end_time": 97260.0,
      "text": "and early access to counsel --"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 97260.0,
      "end_time": 99260.0,
      "text": "it is what happens most of the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 99260.0,
      "end_time": 101260.0,
      "text": "I believe today that it is possible for us"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 101260.0,
      "end_time": 104260.0,
      "text": "as a world community, if we make a decision,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 104260.0,
      "end_time": 106260.0,
      "text": "to come together and end torture"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 106260.0,
      "end_time": 109260.0,
      "text": "as an investigative tool in our lifetime,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 109260.0,
      "end_time": 111260.0,
      "text": "but it will require three things."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 111260.0,
      "end_time": 114260.0,
      "text": "First is the training, empowerment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 114260.0,
      "end_time": 117260.0,
      "text": "and connection of defenders worldwide."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 117260.0,
      "end_time": 120260.0,
      "text": "The second is insuring that there is"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 120260.0,
      "end_time": 123260.0,
      "text": "systematic early access to counsel."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 123260.0,
      "end_time": 126260.0,
      "text": "And the third is commitment."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 126260.0,
      "end_time": 128259.0,
      "text": "So in the year 2000,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 128258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 131260.0,
      "text": "I began to wonder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 131260.0,
      "end_time": 134260.0,
      "text": "what if we came together?"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 134260.0,
      "end_time": 136260.0,
      "text": "Could we do something"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 136260.0,
      "end_time": 138260.0,
      "text": "for these 93 countries?"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 138260.0,
      "end_time": 140260.0,
      "text": "And I founded International Bridges to Justice"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 140260.0,
      "end_time": 142260.0,
      "text": "which has a specific mission of"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 142260.0,
      "end_time": 145260.0,
      "text": "ending torture as an investigative tool"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 145260.0,
      "end_time": 147260.0,
      "text": "and implementing due process rights"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 147260.0,
      "end_time": 150260.0,
      "text": "in the 93 countries by placing trained lawyers"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 150260.0,
      "end_time": 152260.0,
      "text": "at an early stage in police stations"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 152260.0,
      "end_time": 154260.0,
      "text": "and in courtrooms."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 154260.0,
      "end_time": 156260.0,
      "text": "My first experiences, though, did come"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 156260.0,
      "end_time": 159260.0,
      "text": "from Cambodia, and at the time I remember"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 159260.0,
      "end_time": 161260.0,
      "text": "first coming to Cambodia and there were,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 161260.0,
      "end_time": 163260.0,
      "text": "in 1994, still less than"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 163260.0,
      "end_time": 165260.0,
      "text": "10 attorneys in the country because"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 165260.0,
      "end_time": 167260.0,
      "text": "the Khmer Rouge had killed them all."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 167260.0,
      "end_time": 169260.0,
      "text": "And even 20 years later, there was only"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 169260.0,
      "end_time": 171260.0,
      "text": "10 lawyers in the country, so consequently"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 171260.0,
      "end_time": 173260.0,
      "text": "you&#39;d walk into a prison and"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 173260.0,
      "end_time": 175260.0,
      "text": "not only would you meet 12-year-old boys,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 175260.0,
      "end_time": 177260.0,
      "text": "you&#39;d meet women and you&#39;d say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 177260.0,
      "end_time": 179260.0,
      "text": "\"Why are you here?\" Women would say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 179260.0,
      "end_time": 181260.0,
      "text": "\"Well I&#39;ve been here for 10 years because"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 181260.0,
      "end_time": 183260.0,
      "text": "my husband committed a crime, but they can&#39;t find him.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 183260.0,
      "end_time": 186260.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s just a place where there was no rule of law."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 186260.0,
      "end_time": 188260.0,
      "text": "The first group of defenders came together"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 188260.0,
      "end_time": 190260.0,
      "text": "and I still remember, as I was training, I said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 190260.0,
      "end_time": 192260.0,
      "text": "\"Okay, what do you do for an investigation?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 192260.0,
      "end_time": 194260.0,
      "text": "And there was silence in the class, and finally"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 194260.0,
      "end_time": 196260.0,
      "text": "one woman stood up, [inaudible name],"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 196260.0,
      "end_time": 199260.0,
      "text": "and she said \"Khrew,\" which means \"teacher.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 199260.0,
      "end_time": 202260.0,
      "text": "She said, \"I have defended more than"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 202260.0,
      "end_time": 205260.0,
      "text": "a hundred people, and I&#39;ve never had to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 205260.0,
      "end_time": 207260.0,
      "text": "any investigation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 207260.0,
      "end_time": 209260.0,
      "text": "because they all come with confessions.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 209260.0,
      "end_time": 212260.0,
      "text": "And we talked about, as a class, the fact that"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 212260.0,
      "end_time": 214260.0,
      "text": "number one, the confessions"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 214260.0,
      "end_time": 216260.0,
      "text": "might not be reliable, but number two,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 216260.0,
      "end_time": 218260.0,
      "text": "we did not want to encourage the police"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 218260.0,
      "end_time": 220260.0,
      "text": "to keep doing this, especially"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 220260.0,
      "end_time": 222260.0,
      "text": "as it was now against the law."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 222260.0,
      "end_time": 224260.0,
      "text": "And it took a lot of courage for these"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 224260.0,
      "end_time": 226260.0,
      "text": "defenders to decide that they would"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 226260.0,
      "end_time": 228260.0,
      "text": "begin to stand up and support each other"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 228260.0,
      "end_time": 231260.0,
      "text": "in implementing these laws."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 231260.0,
      "end_time": 233260.0,
      "text": "And I still remember the first cases where"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 233260.0,
      "end_time": 235260.0,
      "text": "they came, all 25 together, she would"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 235260.0,
      "end_time": 237260.0,
      "text": "stand up, and they were in the back, and"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 237260.0,
      "end_time": 239260.0,
      "text": "they would support her, and the judges kept"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 239260.0,
      "end_time": 241260.0,
      "text": "saying, \"No, no, no, no, we&#39;re going to do things"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 241260.0,
      "end_time": 243260.0,
      "text": "the exact same way we&#39;ve been doing them.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 243260.0,
      "end_time": 245260.0,
      "text": "But one day the perfect case came, and it"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 245260.0,
      "end_time": 247260.0,
      "text": "was a woman who was a vegetable seller,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 247260.0,
      "end_time": 249260.0,
      "text": "she was sitting outside of a house."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 249260.0,
      "end_time": 252260.0,
      "text": "She said she actually saw the person"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 252260.0,
      "end_time": 254260.0,
      "text": "run out who she thinks stole"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 254260.0,
      "end_time": 256260.0,
      "text": "whatever the jewelry was, but the police"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 256260.0,
      "end_time": 258260.0,
      "text": "came, they got her, there was nothing on her."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 258260.0,
      "end_time": 260260.0,
      "text": "She was pregnant at the time. She had"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 260260.0,
      "end_time": 262260.0,
      "text": "cigarette burns on her. She&#39;d miscarried."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 262260.0,
      "end_time": 264260.0,
      "text": "And when they brought her case"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 264260.0,
      "end_time": 266260.0,
      "text": "to the judge, for the first time he stood up"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 266260.0,
      "end_time": 268260.0,
      "text": "and he said, \"Yes, there&#39;s no evidence"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 268260.0,
      "end_time": 270260.0,
      "text": "except for your torture confession"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 270260.0,
      "end_time": 272260.0,
      "text": "and you will be released.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 272260.0,
      "end_time": 274260.0,
      "text": "And the defenders began to take cases"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 274260.0,
      "end_time": 276260.0,
      "text": "over and over again and"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 276260.0,
      "end_time": 279260.0,
      "text": "you will see, they have step by step began"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 279260.0,
      "end_time": 282260.0,
      "text": "to change the course of history in Cambodia."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 282260.0,
      "end_time": 284260.0,
      "text": "But Cambodia is not alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 284260.0,
      "end_time": 286260.0,
      "text": "I used to think, well is it Cambodia?"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 286260.0,
      "end_time": 288260.0,
      "text": "Or is it other countries?"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 288260.0,
      "end_time": 291260.0,
      "text": "But it is in so many countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 291260.0,
      "end_time": 293260.0,
      "text": "In Burundi I walked into a prison and it wasn&#39;t"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 293260.0,
      "end_time": 296260.0,
      "text": "a 12-year-old boy, it was an 8-year-old boy"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 296260.0,
      "end_time": 298260.0,
      "text": "for stealing a mobile phone."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 298260.0,
      "end_time": 300260.0,
      "text": "Or a woman, I picked up her baby,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 300260.0,
      "end_time": 303260.0,
      "text": "really cute baby, I said \"Your baby is so cute.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 303260.0,
      "end_time": 305260.0,
      "text": "It wasn&#39;t a baby, she was three."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 305260.0,
      "end_time": 307260.0,
      "text": "And she said \"Yeah, but she&#39;s why I&#39;m here,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 307260.0,
      "end_time": 309260.0,
      "text": "because she was accused of stealing"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 309260.0,
      "end_time": 311260.0,
      "text": "two diapers and an iron for her baby and"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 311260.0,
      "end_time": 313260.0,
      "text": "still had been in prison."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 313260.0,
      "end_time": 315260.0,
      "text": "And when I walked up to the prison director,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 315260.0,
      "end_time": 317260.0,
      "text": "I said, \"You&#39;ve got to let her out."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 317260.0,
      "end_time": 319260.0,
      "text": "A judge would let her out.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 319260.0,
      "end_time": 321260.0,
      "text": "And he said, \"Okay, we can talk about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 321260.0,
      "end_time": 323260.0,
      "text": "but look at my prison. Eighty percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 323260.0,
      "end_time": 325260.0,
      "text": "of the two thousand people here"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 325260.0,
      "end_time": 327260.0,
      "text": "are without a lawyer. What can we do?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 327260.0,
      "end_time": 329260.0,
      "text": "So lawyers began to courageously"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 329260.0,
      "end_time": 332260.0,
      "text": "stand up together to organize a system"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 332260.0,
      "end_time": 334260.0,
      "text": "where they can take cases."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 334260.0,
      "end_time": 336260.0,
      "text": "But we realized that it&#39;s not only the training"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 336260.0,
      "end_time": 338260.0,
      "text": "of the lawyers, but the connection"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 338260.0,
      "end_time": 340260.0,
      "text": "of the lawyers that makes a difference."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 340260.0,
      "end_time": 342260.0,
      "text": "For example, in Cambodia, it was that"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 342260.0,
      "end_time": 344260.0,
      "text": "[inaudible name] did not go alone"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 344260.0,
      "end_time": 346260.0,
      "text": "but she had 24 lawyers with her"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 346260.0,
      "end_time": 348260.0,
      "text": "who stood up together. And in the same way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 348260.0,
      "end_time": 350260.0,
      "text": "in China, they always tell me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 350260.0,
      "end_time": 352260.0,
      "text": "\"It&#39;s like a fresh wind in the desert"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 352260.0,
      "end_time": 354260.0,
      "text": "when we can come together.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 354260.0,
      "end_time": 356260.0,
      "text": "Or in Zimbabwe, where I remember Innocent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 356260.0,
      "end_time": 358260.0,
      "text": "after coming out of a prison where everybody"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 358260.0,
      "end_time": 360260.0,
      "text": "stood up and said, \"I&#39;ve been here"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 360260.0,
      "end_time": 362260.0,
      "text": "for one year, eight years, 12 years"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 362260.0,
      "end_time": 364260.0,
      "text": "without a lawyer,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 364260.0,
      "end_time": 366260.0,
      "text": "he came and we had a training together"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 366260.0,
      "end_time": 369260.0,
      "text": "and he said, \"I have heard it said\" --"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 369260.0,
      "end_time": 371260.0,
      "text": "because he had heard people mumbling"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 371260.0,
      "end_time": 373260.0,
      "text": "and grumbling -- \"I have heard it said that"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 373260.0,
      "end_time": 376260.0,
      "text": "we cannot help to create justice"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 376260.0,
      "end_time": 378260.0,
      "text": "because we do not have the resources.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 378260.0,
      "end_time": 380260.0,
      "text": "And then he said, \"But I want you to know"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 380260.0,
      "end_time": 383260.0,
      "text": "that the lack of resources"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 383260.0,
      "end_time": 385260.0,
      "text": "is never an excuse for injustice.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 385260.0,
      "end_time": 387260.0,
      "text": "And with that, he successfully"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 387260.0,
      "end_time": 390260.0,
      "text": "organized 68 lawyers who have been"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 390260.0,
      "end_time": 392260.0,
      "text": "systematically taking the cases."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 392260.0,
      "end_time": 395260.0,
      "text": "The key that we see, though, is training"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 395260.0,
      "end_time": 397260.0,
      "text": "and then early access."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 397260.0,
      "end_time": 399260.0,
      "text": "I was recently in Egypt, and was inspired"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 399260.0,
      "end_time": 401260.0,
      "text": "to meet with another group of lawyers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 401260.0,
      "end_time": 403260.0,
      "text": "and what they told me is that they said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 403260.0,
      "end_time": 405260.0,
      "text": "\"Hey, look, we don&#39;t have police"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 405260.0,
      "end_time": 407260.0,
      "text": "on the streets now. The police are"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 407260.0,
      "end_time": 409260.0,
      "text": "one of the main reasons why we had"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 409260.0,
      "end_time": 411260.0,
      "text": "the revolution. They were torturing everybody"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 411260.0,
      "end_time": 413260.0,
      "text": "all the time.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 413260.0,
      "end_time": 415260.0,
      "text": "And I said, \"But there&#39;s been tens of millions"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 415260.0,
      "end_time": 417260.0,
      "text": "of dollars that have recently gone in"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 417260.0,
      "end_time": 419260.0,
      "text": "to the development of the legal system here."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 419260.0,
      "end_time": 421260.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s going on?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 421260.0,
      "end_time": 424260.0,
      "text": "I met with one of the development agencies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 424260.0,
      "end_time": 426260.0,
      "text": "and they were training prosecutors"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 426260.0,
      "end_time": 428260.0,
      "text": "and judges, which is the normal bias,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 428260.0,
      "end_time": 430260.0,
      "text": "as opposed to defenders."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 430260.0,
      "end_time": 432260.0,
      "text": "And they showed me a manual which"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 432260.0,
      "end_time": 434260.0,
      "text": "actually was an excellent manual."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 434260.0,
      "end_time": 436260.0,
      "text": "I said, \"I&#39;m gonna copy this.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 436260.0,
      "end_time": 438260.0,
      "text": "It had everything in it. Lawyers can come"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 438260.0,
      "end_time": 440260.0,
      "text": "at the police station. It was perfect."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 440260.0,
      "end_time": 442260.0,
      "text": "Prosecutors were perfectly trained."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 442260.0,
      "end_time": 444260.0,
      "text": "But I said to them, \"I just have one question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 444260.0,
      "end_time": 446260.0,
      "text": "which is, by the time that everybody got to"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 446260.0,
      "end_time": 448260.0,
      "text": "the prosecutor&#39;s office, what had happened to them?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 448260.0,
      "end_time": 450260.0,
      "text": "And after a pause, they said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 450260.0,
      "end_time": 452260.0,
      "text": "\"They had been tortured.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 452260.0,
      "end_time": 454260.0,
      "text": "So the pieces are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 454260.0,
      "end_time": 456260.0,
      "text": "not only the training of the lawyers, but"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 456260.0,
      "end_time": 459260.0,
      "text": "us finding a way to systematically implement"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 459260.0,
      "end_time": 462260.0,
      "text": "early access to counsel, because they are"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 462260.0,
      "end_time": 464260.0,
      "text": "the safeguard in the system"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 464260.0,
      "end_time": 467260.0,
      "text": "for people who are being tortured."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 467260.0,
      "end_time": 469260.0,
      "text": "And as I tell you this, I&#39;m also aware of the"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 469260.0,
      "end_time": 471260.0,
      "text": "fact that it sounds like, \"Oh, okay, it sounds"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 471260.0,
      "end_time": 474260.0,
      "text": "like we could do it, but can we really do it?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 474260.0,
      "end_time": 476260.0,
      "text": "Because it sounds big."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 476260.0,
      "end_time": 479260.0,
      "text": "And there are many reasons why I believe it&#39;s possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 479260.0,
      "end_time": 482260.0,
      "text": "The first reason is the people on the ground"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 482260.0,
      "end_time": 485260.0,
      "text": "who find ways of creating miracles"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 485260.0,
      "end_time": 487260.0,
      "text": "because of their commitment."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 487260.0,
      "end_time": 490260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not only Innocent, who I told you about"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 490260.0,
      "end_time": 493260.0,
      "text": "in Zimbabwe, but defenders all over the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 493260.0,
      "end_time": 496260.0,
      "text": "who are looking for these pieces."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 496260.0,
      "end_time": 499260.0,
      "text": "We have a program called JusticeMakers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 499260.0,
      "end_time": 501260.0,
      "text": "and we realized there are people that are"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 501260.0,
      "end_time": 503260.0,
      "text": "courageous and want to do things, but"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 503260.0,
      "end_time": 505260.0,
      "text": "how can we support them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 505260.0,
      "end_time": 507260.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s an online contest where it&#39;s only"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 507260.0,
      "end_time": 509260.0,
      "text": "five thousand dollars if you come up with"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 509260.0,
      "end_time": 511260.0,
      "text": "and innovative way of implementing justice."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 511260.0,
      "end_time": 513260.0,
      "text": "And there are 30 JusticeMakers"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 513260.0,
      "end_time": 515260.0,
      "text": "throughout the world, from Sri Lanka"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 515260.0,
      "end_time": 518260.0,
      "text": "to Swaziland to the DRC, who with"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 518260.0,
      "end_time": 521260.0,
      "text": "five thousand dollars do amazing things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 521260.0,
      "end_time": 523260.0,
      "text": "through SMS programs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 523260.0,
      "end_time": 525260.0,
      "text": "through paralegal programs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 525260.0,
      "end_time": 527260.0,
      "text": "through whatever they can do."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 527260.0,
      "end_time": 531260.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s not only these JusticeMakers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 531260.0,
      "end_time": 533260.0,
      "text": "but people we courageously see"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 533260.0,
      "end_time": 536260.0,
      "text": "figure out who their networks are"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 536260.0,
      "end_time": 538260.0,
      "text": "and how they can move it forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 538260.0,
      "end_time": 540260.0,
      "text": "So in China, for instance, great laws"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 540260.0,
      "end_time": 543260.0,
      "text": "came out where it says police cannot"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 543260.0,
      "end_time": 546260.0,
      "text": "torture people or they will be punished."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 546260.0,
      "end_time": 549260.0,
      "text": "And I was sitting side by side with one of our"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 549260.0,
      "end_time": 552260.0,
      "text": "very courageous lawyers, and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 552260.0,
      "end_time": 554260.0,
      "text": "\"How can we get this out? How can we"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 554260.0,
      "end_time": 556260.0,
      "text": "make sure that this is implemented?"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 556260.0,
      "end_time": 558260.0,
      "text": "This is fantastic.\" And he said to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 558260.0,
      "end_time": 560260.0,
      "text": "\"Well, do you have money?\" And I said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 560260.0,
      "end_time": 562260.0,
      "text": "\"No.\" And he said, \"That&#39;s okay,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 562260.0,
      "end_time": 564260.0,
      "text": "we can still figure it out.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 564260.0,
      "end_time": 566260.0,
      "text": "And on December 4, he organized"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 566260.0,
      "end_time": 568260.0,
      "text": "three thousand members"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 568260.0,
      "end_time": 570260.0,
      "text": "of the Youth Communist League,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 570260.0,
      "end_time": 572260.0,
      "text": "from 14 of the top law schools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 572260.0,
      "end_time": 574260.0,
      "text": "who organized themselves, developed"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 574260.0,
      "end_time": 576260.0,
      "text": "posters with the new laws, and went"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 576260.0,
      "end_time": 578260.0,
      "text": "to the police stations and began what he says"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 578260.0,
      "end_time": 581260.0,
      "text": "is a non-violent legal revolution"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 581260.0,
      "end_time": 584260.0,
      "text": "to protect citizen rights."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 584260.0,
      "end_time": 586260.0,
      "text": "So I talked about the fact that we need"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 586260.0,
      "end_time": 588260.0,
      "text": "to train and support defenders."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 588260.0,
      "end_time": 590260.0,
      "text": "We need to systematically implement"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 590260.0,
      "end_time": 592260.0,
      "text": "early access to counsel."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 592260.0,
      "end_time": 594260.0,
      "text": "But the third and most important thing is that"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 594260.0,
      "end_time": 596260.0,
      "text": "we make a commitment to this."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 596260.0,
      "end_time": 598260.0,
      "text": "And people often say to me, \"You know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 598260.0,
      "end_time": 600260.0,
      "text": "this is great, but it&#39;s wildly idealistic."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 600260.0,
      "end_time": 602260.0,
      "text": "Never going to happen.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 602260.0,
      "end_time": 604260.0,
      "text": "And the reason that I think that"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 604260.0,
      "end_time": 606260.0,
      "text": "those words are interesting is because"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 606260.0,
      "end_time": 608260.0,
      "text": "those were the same kinds of words"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 608260.0,
      "end_time": 610260.0,
      "text": "that were used for people who decided"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 610260.0,
      "end_time": 612260.0,
      "text": "they would end slavery, or end apartheid."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 612260.0,
      "end_time": 614260.0,
      "text": "It began with a small group of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 614260.0,
      "end_time": 616260.0,
      "text": "who decided they would commit."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 616260.0,
      "end_time": 618260.0,
      "text": "Now, there&#39;s one of our favorite poems"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 618260.0,
      "end_time": 620260.0,
      "text": "from the defenders, which they share"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 620260.0,
      "end_time": 622260.0,
      "text": "from each other, is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 622260.0,
      "end_time": 624260.0,
      "text": "\"Take courage friends, the road is often long,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 624260.0,
      "end_time": 626260.0,
      "text": "the path is never clear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 626260.0,
      "end_time": 628260.0,
      "text": "and the stakes are very high,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 628260.0,
      "end_time": 630260.0,
      "text": "but deep down, you are not alone.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 630260.0,
      "end_time": 633260.0,
      "text": "And I believe that if we can come together"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 633260.0,
      "end_time": 635260.0,
      "text": "as a world community to support not only"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 635260.0,
      "end_time": 638260.0,
      "text": "defenders, but also everyone in the system"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 638260.0,
      "end_time": 640260.0,
      "text": "who is looking towards it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 640260.0,
      "end_time": 643260.0,
      "text": "we can end torture as an investigative tool."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 643260.0,
      "end_time": 645260.0,
      "text": "I end always, because I&#39;m sure the questions are --"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 645260.0,
      "end_time": 647260.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;d be happy to talk to you"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 647260.0,
      "end_time": 649260.0,
      "text": "at any point -- \"But what can I really do?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 649260.0,
      "end_time": 651260.0,
      "text": "Well, I would say this. First of all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 651260.0,
      "end_time": 653260.0,
      "text": "you know what you can do. But second of all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 653260.0,
      "end_time": 655260.0,
      "text": "I would leave you with the story of Vishna,"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 655260.0,
      "end_time": 658260.0,
      "text": "who actually was my inspiration"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 658260.0,
      "end_time": 660260.0,
      "text": "for starting International Bridges to Justice."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 660260.0,
      "end_time": 663260.0,
      "text": "Vishna was a 4-year-old boy when I met him"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 663260.0,
      "end_time": 665260.0,
      "text": "who was born in a Cambodian prison"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 665260.0,
      "end_time": 668260.0,
      "text": "in Kandal Province. But because he was"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 668260.0,
      "end_time": 670260.0,
      "text": "born in the prison, everybody loved him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 670260.0,
      "end_time": 672260.0,
      "text": "including the guards, so he was the only one"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 672260.0,
      "end_time": 674260.0,
      "text": "who was allowed to come"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 674260.0,
      "end_time": 676260.0,
      "text": "in and out of the bars."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 676260.0,
      "end_time": 678260.0,
      "text": "So, you know, there&#39;s bars. And by the time"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 678260.0,
      "end_time": 680260.0,
      "text": "that Vishna was getting bigger,"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 680260.0,
      "end_time": 682260.0,
      "text": "which means what gets bigger? Your head gets bigger."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 682260.0,
      "end_time": 684260.0,
      "text": "So he would come to the first bar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 684260.0,
      "end_time": 686260.0,
      "text": "the second bar and then the third bar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 686260.0,
      "end_time": 688260.0,
      "text": "and then really slowly move his head"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 688260.0,
      "end_time": 690260.0,
      "text": "so he could fit through, and come back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 690260.0,
      "end_time": 692260.0,
      "text": "third, second, first. And he would"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 692260.0,
      "end_time": 694260.0,
      "text": "grab my pinkie, because what he wanted"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 694260.0,
      "end_time": 696260.0,
      "text": "to do every day is he wanted to go visit."
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 696260.0,
      "end_time": 698260.0,
      "text": "You know, he never quite made it to"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 698260.0,
      "end_time": 700260.0,
      "text": "all of them every day, but he wanted to visit"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 700260.0,
      "end_time": 702260.0,
      "text": "all 156 prisoners. And I would lift him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 702260.0,
      "end_time": 704260.0,
      "text": "and he would put his fingers through."
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 704260.0,
      "end_time": 706260.0,
      "text": "Or if they were dark cells, it was like iron"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 706260.0,
      "end_time": 708260.0,
      "text": "corrugated, and he would put his fingers through."
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 708260.0,
      "end_time": 710260.0,
      "text": "And most of the prisoners said that he was"
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 710260.0,
      "end_time": 712260.0,
      "text": "their greatest joy and their sunshine, and they"
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 712260.0,
      "end_time": 714260.0,
      "text": "looked forward to him. And I was like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 714260.0,
      "end_time": 716260.0,
      "text": "here&#39;s Vishna. He&#39;s a 4-year-old boy."
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 716260.0,
      "end_time": 718260.0,
      "text": "He was born in a prison with almost nothing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 718260.0,
      "end_time": 720260.0,
      "text": "no material goods, but he had a sense of"
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 720260.0,
      "end_time": 722260.0,
      "text": "his own heroic journey, which I believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 722260.0,
      "end_time": 724260.0,
      "text": "we are all born into. He said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 724260.0,
      "end_time": 726260.0,
      "text": "\"Probably I can&#39;t do everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "start_time": 726260.0,
      "end_time": 728260.0,
      "text": "But I&#39;m one. I can do something."
    },
    {
      "index": 323,
      "start_time": 728260.0,
      "end_time": 730260.0,
      "text": "And I will do the one thing that I can do.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 324,
      "start_time": 730260.0,
      "end_time": 732260.0,
      "text": "So I thank you for having the prophetic"
    },
    {
      "index": 325,
      "start_time": 732260.0,
      "end_time": 735260.0,
      "text": "imagination to imagine the shaping"
    },
    {
      "index": 326,
      "start_time": 735260.0,
      "end_time": 737260.0,
      "text": "of a new world with us together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 327,
      "start_time": 737260.0,
      "end_time": 739260.0,
      "text": "and invite you into this journey with us."
    },
    {
      "index": 328,
      "start_time": 739260.0,
      "end_time": 741260.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 329,
      "start_time": 741260.0,
      "end_time": 749260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 330,
      "start_time": 749260.0,
      "end_time": 751260.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 331,
      "start_time": 751260.0,
      "end_time": 753260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 332,
      "start_time": 753260.0,
      "end_time": 755260.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 333,
      "start_time": 755260.0,
      "end_time": 757260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}